{
  "video_id": "ajGgd9Ld-Wc",
  "title": "How AI can save our humanity | Kai-Fu Lee",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12640.0,
      "end_time": 17176.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to talk about how AI and mankind can coexist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17200.0,
      "end_time": 21160.0,
      "text": "but first, we have to rethink about our human values."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21400.0,
      "end_time": 25360.0,
      "text": "So let me first make a confession about my errors in my values."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25920.0,
      "end_time": 30176.0,
      "text": "It was 11 o&#39;clock, December 16, 1991."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 30200.0,
      "end_time": 32880.0,
      "text": "I was about to become a father for the first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 33480.0,
      "end_time": 36336.0,
      "text": "My wife, Shen-Ling, lay in the hospital bed"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 36360.0,
      "end_time": 39440.0,
      "text": "going through a very difficult 12-hour labor."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 40280.0,
      "end_time": 42576.0,
      "text": "I sat by her bedside"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 42600.0,
      "end_time": 44976.0,
      "text": "but looked anxiously at my watch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45000.0,
      "end_time": 46800.0,
      "text": "and I knew something that she didn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 47440.0,
      "end_time": 49239.0,
      "text": "I knew that if in one hour,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 50360.0,
      "end_time": 52296.0,
      "text": "our child didn&#39;t come,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52320.0,
      "end_time": 54256.0,
      "text": "I was going to leave her there"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 54280.0,
      "end_time": 55936.0,
      "text": "and go back to work"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55960.0,
      "end_time": 58536.0,
      "text": "and make a presentation about AI"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 58560.0,
      "end_time": 60760.0,
      "text": "to my boss, Apple&#39;s CEO."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 63160.0,
      "end_time": 67560.0,
      "text": "Fortunately, my daughter was born at 11:30 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 67800.0,
      "end_time": 69150.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 69400.0,
      "end_time": 70976.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 71000.0,
      "end_time": 75336.0,
      "text": "sparing me from doing the unthinkable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 75360.0,
      "end_time": 77856.0,
      "text": "and to this day, I am so sorry"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 77880.0,
      "end_time": 82536.0,
      "text": "for letting my work ethic take precedence over love for my family."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82560.0,
      "end_time": 88296.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88320.0,
      "end_time": 90936.0,
      "text": "My AI talk, however, went off brilliantly."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 90960.0,
      "end_time": 93696.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 93720.0,
      "end_time": 96856.0,
      "text": "Apple loved my work and decided to announce it"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 96880.0,
      "end_time": 99576.0,
      "text": "at TED1992,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 99600.0,
      "end_time": 102616.0,
      "text": "26 years ago on this very stage."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 102640.0,
      "end_time": 107696.0,
      "text": "I thought I had made one of the biggest, most important discoveries in AI,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 107720.0,
      "end_time": 110640.0,
      "text": "and so did the \"Wall Street Journal\" on the following day."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 111440.0,
      "end_time": 113976.0,
      "text": "But as far as discoveries went,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 114000.0,
      "end_time": 115336.0,
      "text": "it turned out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 115360.0,
      "end_time": 118136.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t discover India, or America."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 118160.0,
      "end_time": 121240.0,
      "text": "Perhaps I discovered a little island off of Portugal."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 122720.0,
      "end_time": 125976.0,
      "text": "But the AI era of discovery continued,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 126000.0,
      "end_time": 129216.0,
      "text": "and more scientists poured their souls into it."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 129240.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131856.0,
      "text": "About 10 years ago, the grand AI discovery"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 131880.0,
      "end_time": 135550.0,
      "text": "was made by three North American scientists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 135800.0,
      "end_time": 136680.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s known as deep learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 137400.0,
      "end_time": 141960.0,
      "text": "Deep learning is a technology that can take a huge amount of data"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 141120.0,
      "end_time": 142856.0,
      "text": "within one single domain"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 142880.0,
      "end_time": 147816.0,
      "text": "and learn to predict or decide at superhuman accuracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 147840.0,
      "end_time": 150616.0,
      "text": "For example, if we show the deep learning network"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 150640.0,
      "end_time": 153456.0,
      "text": "a massive number of food photos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 153480.0,
      "end_time": 155550.0,
      "text": "it can recognize food"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 155800.0,
      "end_time": 158376.0,
      "text": "such as hot dog or no hot dog."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 158400.0,
      "end_time": 161536.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 161560.0,
      "end_time": 166576.0,
      "text": "Or if we show it many pictures and videos and sensor data"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 166600.0,
      "end_time": 169136.0,
      "text": "from driving on the highway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 169160.0,
      "end_time": 172440.0,
      "text": "it can actually drive a car as well as a human being"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 173360.0,
      "end_time": 175160.0,
      "text": "on the highway."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 175400.0,
      "end_time": 177856.0,
      "text": "And what if we showed this deep learning network"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 177880.0,
      "end_time": 180280.0,
      "text": "all the speeches made by President Trump?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 181680.0,
      "end_time": 184680.0,
      "text": "Then this artificially intelligent President Trump,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 185600.0,
      "end_time": 187816.0,
      "text": "actually the network --"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 187840.0,
      "end_time": 189496.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 189520.0,
      "end_time": 190736.0,
      "text": "can --"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 190760.0,
      "end_time": 194816.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 194840.0,
      "end_time": 197176.0,
      "text": "You like double oxymorons, huh?"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 197200.0,
      "end_time": 201550.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 201800.0,
      "end_time": 207176.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 207200.0,
      "end_time": 212456.0,
      "text": "So this network, if given the request to make a speech about AI,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 212480.0,
      "end_time": 215119.0,
      "text": "he, or it, might say --"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 216280.0,
      "end_time": 218376.0,
      "text": "(Recording) Donald Trump: It&#39;s a great thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 218400.0,
      "end_time": 221336.0,
      "text": "to build a better world with artificial intelligence."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 221360.0,
      "end_time": 223376.0,
      "text": "Kai-Fu Lee: And maybe in another language?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 223400.0,
      "end_time": 225216.0,
      "text": "DT: (Speaking Chinese)"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 225240.0,
      "end_time": 226736.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 226760.0,
      "end_time": 228920.0,
      "text": "KFL: You didn&#39;t know he knew Chinese, did you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 230120.0,
      "end_time": 235136.0,
      "text": "So deep learning has become the core in the era of AI discovery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 235160.0,
      "end_time": 236976.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s led by the US."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 237000.0,
      "end_time": 240256.0,
      "text": "But we&#39;re now in the era of implementation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 240280.0,
      "end_time": 245816.0,
      "text": "where what really matters is execution, product quality, speed and data."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 245840.0,
      "end_time": 247936.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s where China comes in."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 247960.0,
      "end_time": 249536.0,
      "text": "Chinese entrepreneurs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 249560.0,
      "end_time": 251456.0,
      "text": "who I fund as a venture capitalist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 251480.0,
      "end_time": 253215.0,
      "text": "are incredible workers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 253240.0,
      "end_time": 255176.0,
      "text": "amazing work ethic."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 255200.0,
      "end_time": 260495.0,
      "text": "My example in the delivery room is nothing compared to how hard people work in China."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 260519.0,
      "end_time": 264216.0,
      "text": "As an example, one startup tried to claim work-life balance:"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 264240.0,
      "end_time": 267936.0,
      "text": "\"Come work for us because we are 996.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 267960.0,
      "end_time": 269215.0,
      "text": "And what does that mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 269240.0,
      "end_time": 273640.0,
      "text": "It means the work hours of 9am to 9pm, six days a week."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 274960.0,
      "end_time": 278239.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s contrasted with other startups that do 997."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 279320.0,
      "end_time": 282416.0,
      "text": "And the Chinese product quality has consistently gone up"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 282440.0,
      "end_time": 284136.0,
      "text": "in the past decade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 284160.0,
      "end_time": 288280.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s because of a fiercely competitive environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 288760.0,
      "end_time": 294656.0,
      "text": "In Silicon Valley, entrepreneurs compete in a very gentlemanly fashion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 294680.0,
      "end_time": 298576.0,
      "text": "sort of like in old wars in which each side took turns"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 298600.0,
      "end_time": 299856.0,
      "text": "to fire at each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 299880.0,
      "end_time": 300936.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 300960.0,
      "end_time": 302976.0,
      "text": "But in the Chinese environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 303000.0,
      "end_time": 305880.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s truly a gladiatorial fight to the death."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 306920.0,
      "end_time": 313160.0,
      "text": "In such a brutal environment, entrepreneurs learn to grow very rapidly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 313400.0,
      "end_time": 316976.0,
      "text": "they learn to make their products better at lightning speed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 317000.0,
      "end_time": 319336.0,
      "text": "and they learn to hone their business models"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 319360.0,
      "end_time": 320760.0,
      "text": "until they&#39;re impregnable."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 321400.0,
      "end_time": 325256.0,
      "text": "As a result, great Chinese products like WeChat and Weibo"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 325280.0,
      "end_time": 326695.0,
      "text": "are arguably better"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 326720.0,
      "end_time": 330200.0,
      "text": "than the equivalent American products from Facebook and Twitter."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 331920.0,
      "end_time": 335160.0,
      "text": "And the Chinese market embraces this change"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 335400.0,
      "end_time": 338560.0,
      "text": "and accelerated change and paradigm shifts."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 338800.0,
      "end_time": 340176.0,
      "text": "As an example, if any of you go to China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 340200.0,
      "end_time": 344216.0,
      "text": "you will see it&#39;s almost cashless and credit card-less,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 344240.0,
      "end_time": 346976.0,
      "text": "because that thing that we all talk about, mobile payment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 347000.0,
      "end_time": 349416.0,
      "text": "has become the reality in China."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 349440.0,
      "end_time": 350736.0,
      "text": "In the last year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 350760.0,
      "end_time": 356695.0,
      "text": "18.8 trillion US dollars were transacted on mobile internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 356720.0,
      "end_time": 359656.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s because of very robust technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 359680.0,
      "end_time": 360936.0,
      "text": "built behind it."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 360960.0,
      "end_time": 363400.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s even bigger than the China GDP."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 364120.0,
      "end_time": 367736.0,
      "text": "And this technology, you can say, how can it be bigger than the GDP?"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 367760.0,
      "end_time": 369736.0,
      "text": "Because it includes all transactions:"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 369760.0,
      "end_time": 373536.0,
      "text": "wholesale, channels, retail, online, offline,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 373560.0,
      "end_time": 378616.0,
      "text": "going into a shopping mall or going into a farmers market like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 378640.0,
      "end_time": 382150.0,
      "text": "The technology is used by 700 million people"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 382400.0,
      "end_time": 384960.0,
      "text": "to pay each other, not just merchants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 384120.0,
      "end_time": 385536.0,
      "text": "so it&#39;s peer to peer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 385560.0,
      "end_time": 388240.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s almost transaction-fee-free."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 389720.0,
      "end_time": 392960.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s instantaneous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 392120.0,
      "end_time": 393560.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s used everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 394320.0,
      "end_time": 397695.0,
      "text": "And finally, the China market is enormous."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 397720.0,
      "end_time": 399696.0,
      "text": "This market is large,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 399720.0,
      "end_time": 404216.0,
      "text": "which helps give entrepreneurs more users, more revenue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 404240.0,
      "end_time": 406576.0,
      "text": "more investment, but most importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 406600.0,
      "end_time": 411136.0,
      "text": "it gives the entrepreneurs a chance to collect a huge amount of data"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 411160.0,
      "end_time": 414120.0,
      "text": "which becomes rocket fuel for the AI engine."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 414960.0,
      "end_time": 417895.0,
      "text": "So as a result, the Chinese AI companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 417920.0,
      "end_time": 419656.0,
      "text": "have leaped ahead"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 419680.0,
      "end_time": 422776.0,
      "text": "so that today, the most valuable companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 422800.0,
      "end_time": 425416.0,
      "text": "in computer vision, speech recognition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 425440.0,
      "end_time": 428856.0,
      "text": "speech synthesis, machine translation and drones"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 428880.0,
      "end_time": 430800.0,
      "text": "are all Chinese companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 431400.0,
      "end_time": 434616.0,
      "text": "So with the US leading the era of discovery"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 434640.0,
      "end_time": 437776.0,
      "text": "and China leading the era of implementation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 437800.0,
      "end_time": 440560.0,
      "text": "we are now in an amazing age"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 440800.0,
      "end_time": 443335.0,
      "text": "where the dual engine of the two superpowers"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 443360.0,
      "end_time": 445400.0,
      "text": "are working together"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 445960.0,
      "end_time": 449616.0,
      "text": "to drive the fastest revolution in technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 449640.0,
      "end_time": 452000.0,
      "text": "that we have ever seen as humans."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 452640.0,
      "end_time": 455135.0,
      "text": "And this will bring tremendous wealth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 455160.0,
      "end_time": 456936.0,
      "text": "unprecedented wealth:"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 456960.0,
      "end_time": 460856.0,
      "text": "16 trillion dollars, according to PwC,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 460880.0,
      "end_time": 466256.0,
      "text": "in terms of added GDP to the worldwide GDP by 2030."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 466280.0,
      "end_time": 468895.0,
      "text": "It will also bring immense challenges"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 468920.0,
      "end_time": 472496.0,
      "text": "in terms of potential job replacements."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 472520.0,
      "end_time": 474680.0,
      "text": "Whereas in the Industrial Age"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 475880.0,
      "end_time": 477416.0,
      "text": "it created more jobs"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 477440.0,
      "end_time": 483216.0,
      "text": "because craftsman jobs were being decomposed into jobs in the assembly line,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 483240.0,
      "end_time": 485216.0,
      "text": "so more jobs were created."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 485240.0,
      "end_time": 490176.0,
      "text": "But AI completely replaces the individual jobs"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 490200.0,
      "end_time": 492455.0,
      "text": "in the assembly line with robots."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 492480.0,
      "end_time": 494416.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not just in factories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 494440.0,
      "end_time": 496496.0,
      "text": "but truckers, drivers"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 496520.0,
      "end_time": 500616.0,
      "text": "and even jobs like telesales, customer service"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 500640.0,
      "end_time": 503616.0,
      "text": "and hematologists as well as radiologists"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 503640.0,
      "end_time": 505736.0,
      "text": "over the next 15 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 505760.0,
      "end_time": 508296.0,
      "text": "are going to be gradually replaced"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 508320.0,
      "end_time": 509760.0,
      "text": "by artificial intelligence."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 510360.0,
      "end_time": 512416.0,
      "text": "And only the creative jobs --"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 512440.00000000006,
      "end_time": 514416.00000000006,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 514440.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516640.00000000006,
      "text": "I have to make myself safe, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 518960.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521936.00000000006,
      "text": "Really, the creative jobs are the ones that are protected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 521960.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525000.0,
      "text": "because AI can optimize but not create."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 525960.0,
      "end_time": 529535.0,
      "text": "But what&#39;s more serious than the loss of jobs"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 529559.0,
      "end_time": 531336.0,
      "text": "is the loss of meaning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 531360.0,
      "end_time": 534496.0,
      "text": "because the work ethic in the Industrial Age"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 534520.0,
      "end_time": 540136.0,
      "text": "has brainwashed us into thinking that work is the reason we exist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 540160.0,
      "end_time": 543960.0,
      "text": "that work defined the meaning of our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 543120.0,
      "end_time": 549416.0,
      "text": "And I was a prime and willing victim to that type of workaholic thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 549440.0,
      "end_time": 551560.0,
      "text": "I worked incredibly hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 551800.0,
      "end_time": 554656.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why I almost left my wife in the delivery room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 554680.0,
      "end_time": 558856.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s why I worked 996 alongside my entrepreneurs."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 558880.0,
      "end_time": 563296.0,
      "text": "And that obsession that I had with work"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 563320.0,
      "end_time": 566376.0,
      "text": "ended abruptly a few years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 566400.0,
      "end_time": 570319.0,
      "text": "when I was diagnosed with fourth stage lymphoma."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 571480.0,
      "end_time": 575616.0,
      "text": "The PET scan here shows over 20 malignant tumors"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 575640.0,
      "end_time": 577816.0,
      "text": "jumping out like fireballs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 577840.0,
      "end_time": 580416.0,
      "text": "melting away my ambition."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 580440.0,
      "end_time": 581896.0,
      "text": "But more importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 581920.0,
      "end_time": 584656.0,
      "text": "it helped me reexamine my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 584680.0,
      "end_time": 587776.0,
      "text": "Knowing that I may only have a few months to live"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 587800.0,
      "end_time": 590736.0,
      "text": "caused me to see how foolish it was"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 590760.0,
      "end_time": 594336.0,
      "text": "for me to base my entire self-worth"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 594360.0,
      "end_time": 598400.0,
      "text": "on how hard I worked and the accomplishments from hard work."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 599320.0,
      "end_time": 602296.0,
      "text": "My priorities were completely out of order."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 602320.0,
      "end_time": 603920.0,
      "text": "I neglected my family."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 605000.0,
      "end_time": 606416.0,
      "text": "My father had passed away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 606440.0,
      "end_time": 609240.0,
      "text": "and I never had a chance to tell him I loved him."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 610120.0,
      "end_time": 613856.0,
      "text": "My mother had dementia and no longer recognized me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 613880.0,
      "end_time": 615800.0,
      "text": "and my children had grown up."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 616400.0,
      "end_time": 618550.0,
      "text": "During my chemotherapy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 618800.0,
      "end_time": 620536.0,
      "text": "I read a book by Bronnie Ware"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 620560.0,
      "end_time": 626550.0,
      "text": "who talked about dying wishes and regrets of the people in the deathbed."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 626800.0,
      "end_time": 628336.0,
      "text": "She found that facing death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 628360.0,
      "end_time": 631960.0,
      "text": "nobody regretted that they didn&#39;t work hard enough in this life."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 632880.0,
      "end_time": 638560.0,
      "text": "They only regretted that they didn&#39;t spend enough time with their loved ones"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 638800.0,
      "end_time": 640840.0,
      "text": "and that they didn&#39;t spread their love."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 642400.0,
      "end_time": 646935.0,
      "text": "So I am fortunately today in remission."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 646960.0,
      "end_time": 653816.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 653840.0,
      "end_time": 655816.0,
      "text": "So I can be back at TED again"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 655840.0,
      "end_time": 659216.0,
      "text": "to share with you that I have changed my ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 659240.0,
      "end_time": 662000.0,
      "text": "I now only work 965 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 663200.0,
      "end_time": 667176.0,
      "text": "occasionally 996, but usually 965."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 667200.0,
      "end_time": 669960.0,
      "text": "I moved closer to my mother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 669120.0,
      "end_time": 671576.0,
      "text": "my wife usually travels with me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 671600.0,
      "end_time": 675416.0,
      "text": "and when my kids have vacation, if they don&#39;t come home, I go to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 675440.0,
      "end_time": 677896.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s a new form of life"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 677920.0,
      "end_time": 679736.0,
      "text": "that helped me recognize"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 679760.0,
      "end_time": 682936.0,
      "text": "how important it is that love is for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 682960.0,
      "end_time": 686376.0,
      "text": "and facing death helped me change my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 686400.0,
      "end_time": 688856.0,
      "text": "but it also helped me see a new way"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 688880.0,
      "end_time": 692656.0,
      "text": "of how AI should impact mankind"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 692680.0,
      "end_time": 695160.0,
      "text": "and work and coexist with mankind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 696680.0,
      "end_time": 701175.0,
      "text": "that really, AI is taking away a lot of routine jobs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 701200.0,
      "end_time": 704856.0,
      "text": "but routine jobs are not what we&#39;re about."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 704880.0,
      "end_time": 707136.0,
      "text": "Why we exist is love."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 707160.0,
      "end_time": 709256.0,
      "text": "When we hold our newborn baby,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 709280.0,
      "end_time": 710776.0,
      "text": "love at first sight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 710800.0,
      "end_time": 712575.0,
      "text": "or when we help someone in need,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 712600.0,
      "end_time": 716856.0,
      "text": "humans are uniquely able to give and receive love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 716880.0,
      "end_time": 719680.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s what differentiates us from AI."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 720800.0,
      "end_time": 723496.0,
      "text": "Despite what science fiction may portray,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 723520.0,
      "end_time": 727256.0,
      "text": "I can responsibly tell you that AI has no love."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 727280.0,
      "end_time": 730815.0,
      "text": "When AlphaGo defeated the world champion Ke Jie,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 730840.0,
      "end_time": 733936.0,
      "text": "while Ke Jie was crying and loving the game of go,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 733960.0,
      "end_time": 737136.0,
      "text": "AlphaGo felt no happiness from winning"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 737160.0,
      "end_time": 741640.0,
      "text": "and certainly no desire to hug a loved one."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 743600.0,
      "end_time": 746256.0,
      "text": "So how do we differentiate ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 746280.0,
      "end_time": 748815.0,
      "text": "as humans in the age of AI?"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 748840.0,
      "end_time": 751936.0,
      "text": "We talked about the axis of creativity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 751960.0,
      "end_time": 754816.0,
      "text": "and certainly that is one possibility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 754840.0,
      "end_time": 757136.0,
      "text": "and now we introduce a new axis"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 757160.0,
      "end_time": 760776.0,
      "text": "that we can call compassion, love, or empathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 760800.0,
      "end_time": 763376.0,
      "text": "Those are things that AI cannot do."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 763400.0,
      "end_time": 766216.0,
      "text": "So as AI takes away the routine jobs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 766240.0,
      "end_time": 771200.0,
      "text": "I like to think we can, we should and we must create jobs of compassion."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 771800.0,
      "end_time": 774136.0,
      "text": "You might ask how many of those there are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 774160.0,
      "end_time": 775776.0,
      "text": "but I would ask you:"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 775800.0,
      "end_time": 779616.0,
      "text": "Do you not think that we are going to need a lot of social workers"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 779640.0,
      "end_time": 781240.0,
      "text": "to help us make this transition?"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 781960.0,
      "end_time": 785216.0,
      "text": "Do you not think we need a lot of compassionate caregivers"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 785240.0,
      "end_time": 787936.0,
      "text": "to give more medical care to more people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 787960.0,
      "end_time": 791216.0,
      "text": "Do you not think we&#39;re going to need 10 times more teachers"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 791240.0,
      "end_time": 794160.0,
      "text": "to help our children find their way"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 794400.0,
      "end_time": 797295.0,
      "text": "to survive and thrive in this brave new world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 797320.0,
      "end_time": 799760.0,
      "text": "And with all the newfound wealth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 799800.0,
      "end_time": 804335.0,
      "text": "should we not also make labors of love into careers"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 804360.0,
      "end_time": 807560.0,
      "text": "and let elderly accompaniment"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 807800.0,
      "end_time": 810576.0,
      "text": "or homeschooling become careers also?"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 810600.0,
      "end_time": 815880.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 816800.0,
      "end_time": 819550.0,
      "text": "This graph is surely not perfect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 819800.0,
      "end_time": 822616.0,
      "text": "but it points at four ways that we can work with AI."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 822640.0,
      "end_time": 826216.0,
      "text": "AI will come and take away the routine jobs"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 826240.0,
      "end_time": 828280.0,
      "text": "and in due time, we will be thankful."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 829000.0,
      "end_time": 832960.0,
      "text": "AI will become great tools for the creatives"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 832120.0,
      "end_time": 835776.0,
      "text": "so that scientists, artists, musicians and writers"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 835800.0,
      "end_time": 837400.0,
      "text": "can be even more creative."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 838120.0,
      "end_time": 843496.0,
      "text": "AI will work with humans as analytical tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 843520.0,
      "end_time": 846216.0,
      "text": "that humans can wrap their warmth around"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 846240.0,
      "end_time": 848136.0,
      "text": "for the high-compassion jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 848160.0,
      "end_time": 850815.0,
      "text": "And we can always differentiate ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 850840.0,
      "end_time": 852656.0,
      "text": "with the uniquely capable jobs"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 852680.0,
      "end_time": 856295.0,
      "text": "that are both compassionate and creative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 856320.0,
      "end_time": 861496.0,
      "text": "using and leveraging our irreplaceable brains and hearts."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 861520.0,
      "end_time": 862816.0,
      "text": "So there you have it:"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 862840.0,
      "end_time": 866480.0,
      "text": "a blueprint of coexistence for humans and AI."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 867400.0,
      "end_time": 869216.0,
      "text": "AI is serendipity."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 869240.0,
      "end_time": 872216.0,
      "text": "It is here to liberate us from routine jobs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 872240.0,
      "end_time": 875920.0,
      "text": "and it is here to remind us what it is that makes us human."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 876440.0,
      "end_time": 880416.0,
      "text": "So let us choose to embrace AI and to love one another."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 880440.0,
      "end_time": 881656.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 881680.0,
      "end_time": 887839.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}